#

Herbed Boiled Potatoes

30 min
$5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodSide Dish

Description

Perfectly boiled potatoes with a hint of herbs, simple yet delicious!

Ingredients

  • potatoes: 2 pounds
  • salt: 1 tablespoon
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • fresh parsley: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
